'''''Silver Shadows''''' by [[Elaine Cunningham]] is the third book in the [[Songs & Swords]] series and the thirteenth book in [[The Harpers series]].

{{Quote|''[[Arilyn Moonblade]] has always feared the elfshadow, the essence of her sword's magic. When she learns the terrible truth behind her inherited moonblade, she vows to find a way to escape her fate.''

''What begins as a means to an end becomes a deeply personal commitment. Determined to succeed in her quest, Arilyn will risk all she holds dear.''}}
